            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Antonis Galoga made this work for the salvation of George.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>"… the precise nature of the building is unknown, though judging by the
                    north-east orientation of the four Greek inscriptions recovered, as well as
                    their apparent Christian context, it was in all probability a funerary
                    chapel."</p>
            </div>
